Provides cities json/jsonp data for world cities in the form:
{
  "london":
    {"lat":51.5,"lon":-0.117,"wikipedia":"London","city":"London"},
  "melbourne":
    {"lat":-37.8,"lon":144.95,"wikipedia":"Melbourne","city":"Melbourne"},
  "sanfrancisco":
    {"lat":37.767,"lon":-122.417,"wikipedia":"San_Francisco","city":"San Francisco"}
  "tokyo":
    {"lat":35.683,"lon":139.767,"wikipedia":"Tokyo","city":"Tokyo"},
}

City data sourced from http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_cities_by_longitude, the HTML massaged in Vim to cities.txt included here, and parsed to create cities.jsonp.
